Package com.gcu.agms.service.gate

Interface GateManagementService

All Known Implementing Classes:
JdbcGateManagementService
public interface GateManagementService
Defines the contract for managing airport gates. This service handles the creation, retrieval, updating, and deletion of gates, serving as the primary interface for gate management operations.
